The paper focuses on improving the performance of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) with cheap convolutions, which are commonly used for memory and computation reduction. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE, cs.DL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
